      <title>戴比尔斯警告钻石在经历了糟糕的一年后复苏将会缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/de-beers-warns-diamond-recovery-will-be-slow-after-terrible-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戴比尔斯预计，陷入困境的钻石市场的复苏将是缓慢而渐进的，因为该行业继续受到中国和美国等主要市场经济增长疲弱的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/de-beers-warns-diamond-recovery-will-be-slow-after-terrible-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:43:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
